item.title: The Never Ending Trauma
item.description:
This is perhaps one of the saddest episodes we've ever done on The Deep. Sophia has experienced far more than her share of grief and trauma. It's completely unjust. But Sophia still has poise and gratitude and she is such a ray of light.


Content warning: This episode discusses the death of a young child.
